# Secure Deployment Runner — environment variables
#
# No API keys are required for core functionality.
# All authentication is handled via SSO/PKCE (planned — see docs/AUTOMATION.md).
#
# Future backend integration variables would be declared here, for example:
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-backend-api.example.com
#   VITE_SCCM_ENDPOINT=https://sccm-server.example.com/api
